                "type": "math",
                "latex": "\\begin{aligned}\n\\cos^2 A+\\cos^2 B+\\cos^2 C \n&= \\frac{1+\\cos 2A}{2} + \\frac{1+\\cos 2B}{2} + \\frac{1+\\cos 2C}{2}\\\\\n&= \\frac{3}{2} + \\frac{1}{2}(\\cos 2A+\\cos 2B+\\cos 2C).\n\\end{aligned}"
